  "page": "A Storm of Swords-Chapter 68",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Sansa VI</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_storm_of_swords\" title=\"A storm of swords\"><img alt=\"AStormOfSwords.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg/220px-AStormOfSwords.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"353\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Drearfort\" title=\"Drearfort\">unnamed tower</a> of House Baelish in the <a href=\"/index.php/Fingers\" title=\"Fingers\">Fingers</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n762 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_61\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 61\">Sansa V</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_67\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 67\">Jaime VIII</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sansa VI</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_69\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 69\">Jon IX</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_80\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 80\">Sansa VII</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Places_and_terms_mentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places and terms mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_68&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Morgaine_le_Fee_alayne_stone.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a7/Morgaine_le_Fee_alayne_stone.jpg/300px-Morgaine_le_Fee_alayne_stone.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a7/Morgaine_le_Fee_alayne_stone.jpg/450px-Morgaine_le_Fee_alayne_stone.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a7/Morgaine_le_Fee_alayne_stone.jpg/600px-Morgaine_le_Fee_alayne_stone.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Morgaine_le_Fee_alayne_stone.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Alayne Stone. © Morgaine le Fee</div></div></div>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa</a> is alarmed to discover that <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Littlefinger</a> has no intention of bringing her home; instead she is being taken to <a href=\"/index.php/The_Vale_of_Arryn\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Vale of Arryn\">the Vale of Arryn</a>. They land at <a href=\"/index.php/Drearfort\" title=\"Drearfort\">the tiny tower</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Baelish\" title=\"House Baelish\">House Baelish</a> that Petyr is lord of, and he stresses that Sansa must use a new name, calling her <a href=\"/index.php/Alayne_Stone\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Alayne Stone\">Alayne Stone</a> so that no one will know who she really is. \n</p><p>She learns that <a href=\"/index.php/Oswell_Kettleblack\" title=\"Oswell Kettleblack\">Oswell</a> is actually the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Kettleblack\" title=\"House Kettleblack\">Kettleblacks</a>' father, and Littlefinger leads her to discern that it was the <a href=\"/index.php/Olenna_Tyrell\" title=\"Olenna Tyrell\">Queen of Thorns</a> who poisoned <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey</a> when she took one of the amethysts from Sansa's hair net. All the plans were arranged by Littlefinger, who met Lady Olenna when he brokered the alliance that joined <a href=\"/index.php/Highgarden\" title=\"Highgarden\">Highgarden</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a>. \n</p><p>Soon after, <a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Arryn\" title=\"Lysa Arryn\">Lysa Arryn</a> arrives with a small retinue, and she insists that Petyr wed her now at his tower instead of the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a>. Lysa wants to make another child with Petyr, after <a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">her father</a> aborted the first child years ago. A drunken <a href=\"/index.php/Marillion\" title=\"Marillion\">Marillion</a> tries to seduce Sansa that night, but <a href=\"/index.php/Lothor_Brune\" title=\"Lothor Brune\">Lothor Brune</a> forces him away. The next morning, Petyr tells Alayne that Lysa now knows the girl's identity. Lysa does not like having Sansa around, although she does wish to marry her niece to her son, <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Arryn\" title=\"Robert Arryn\">Robert</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Character_List_appearing/mentioned\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_68&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List appearing/mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a> (Alayne Stone)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a> (Littlefinger)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Oswell_Kettleblack\" title=\"Oswell Kettleblack\">Oswell Kettleblack</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Olenna_Tyrell\" title=\"Olenna Tyrell\">Olenna Tyrell</a> (Queen of Thorns)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Arryn\" title=\"Lysa Arryn\">Lysa Arryn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lothor_Brune\" title=\"Lothor Brune\">Lothor Brune</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Marillion\" title=\"Marillion\">Marillion</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">Hoster Tully</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Arryn\" title=\"Robert Arryn\">Robert Arryn</a></li></ul>\n</div>\t\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places_and_terms_mentioned\">Places and terms mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_68&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places and terms mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Fingers\" title=\"Fingers\">Fingers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Vale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vale\">Vale</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Kettleblack\" title=\"House Kettleblack\">House Kettleblack</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Highgarden\" title=\"Highgarden\">Highgarden</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_68&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>The synopsis was copied from Aol member vbkorik27 previously at<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20080228051425/members.aol.com/vbkorik27/summary/legend.html\">[1]</a></li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tor.com/blogs/2013/08/a-read-of-ice-and-fire-a-storm-of-swords-part-42\">A Read of Ice and Fire: A Storm of Swords, Part 42</a>. Analyses and summary of the chapter by Leigh Butler.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403134552\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.057 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.211 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 242/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 1096/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 8113/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1352/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.150/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.38 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  196.299      1 -total\n 99.40%  195.123      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter_ASoS\n 98.88%  194.105      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter\n 98.35%  193.069      1 Template:Infobox\n  0.52%    1.028      2 Template:Work_color\n  0.51%    1.008      2 Template:Columns\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:6250-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403134552 and revision id 241738\n -->\n",
